Usage: infinit-volume volume [MODE|--help]
Infinit volume management utility.

Modes:
  create     Create a volume
  delete     Delete a volume locally
  export     Export a volume for someone else to import
  fetch      Fetch a volume from https://beyond.infinit.sh
  import     Import a volume
  list       List volumes
  mount      Mount a volume
  pull       Remove a volume from https://beyond.infinit.sh
  push       Push a volume to https://beyond.infinit.sh
  run        Run a volume
  start      Start a volume through the daemon
  status     Get volume status
  stop       Stop a volume
  update     Update a volume with default run options
  syscall    Syscalls

Options:
  -h, --help                show this help message

